Class PropertySetter<T>

  com.github.wuic.util.PropertySetter<T>
Type Parameters:

Direct Known Subclasses:
PropertySetter.PropertySetterOfBoolean, PropertySetter.PropertySetterOfInteger, PropertySetter.PropertySetterOfObject, PropertySetter.PropertySetterOfString, ProxyUrisPropertySetter, SpriteProviderPropertySetter
public abstract class PropertySetter<T>
extends Object

A property setter is an object which is able to set to a particular AbstractNutDaoBuilder a property. This property is associated to a key specifically supported by the type of setter.

The property setter is generic to allow subclasses to define the real type of value associated to its supported property key.
